readable.content: A black dog leaps from the bank into a body of water , with a field of dry grass in the background . A black dog with a blue collar is jumping into the water . A black lab runs headlong into a lake surrounded by farmland . The black dog is running down the grassy knoll to jump in the water below . The dog is jumping into the lake .
